@page "/info/privacy"
@layout PublicLayout
@attribute [AllowAnonymous]
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization

<PageTitle>Privacy & Data Protection | Aethon</PageTitle>

<div class="d-flex flex-column gap-4" style="max-width:720px; margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4">
        <div class="card-body p-4 p-lg-5">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <span style="font-size:2.5rem;"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill text-primary"></i></span>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="h3 fw-bold mb-0">Privacy &amp; Data Protection</h1>
                    <div class="text-secondary">How we collect, use, and protect your data</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p class="lead text-secondary mb-4">
                This platform is designed with a minimal data collection and processing model.
                Only data required to operate the service is collected and processed.
                No analytics, marketing, or tracking technologies are used.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">Cookies</h2>
            <p>The platform only uses <strong>strictly necessary cookies</strong>. These include:</p>
            <ul class="mb-3">
                <li>Authentication and session cookies (login state)</li>
                <li>Security cookies (e.g. CSRF protection)</li>
                <li>Infrastructure cookies (load balancer, CDN, where applicable)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The platform does <strong>not</strong> use analytics, advertising, tracking, or personalisation cookies.
            No cookie consent banner is required and no consent cookie is set.</p>

            <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Data Collection</h2>
            <p>We collect only what is necessary to operate the platform:</p>
            <ul class="mb-3">
                <li>Account data (email, name)</li>
                <li>Job seeker data (profiles, resumes)</li>
                <li>Recruiter and company data</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Purpose of processing:</strong> providing job platform functionality, enabling job applications
            and recruitment workflows, and maintaining system security and integrity.</p>
            <p><strong>Legal basis (GDPR):</strong> contract (service delivery) and legitimate interest (security, operations).</p>

            <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
            <ul class="mb-3">
                <li>All data is stored in <strong>Australia</strong></li>
                <li>Data is processed using secure infrastructure providers</li>
                <li>Appropriate safeguards are applied where required</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Data Retention</h2>
            <p>Inactivity is measured from the time of last successful login.</p>
            <div class="table-responsive mb-3">
                <table class="table table-bordered rounded-3 overflow-hidden mb-0">
                    <thead class="table-dark">
                        <tr>
                            <th>Account type</th>
                            <th>Warning sent</th>
                            <th>Auto-deleted</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Under 18</td>
                            <td>Day 25</td>
                            <td>Day 30</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>18 and over</td>
                            <td>Day 80</td>
                            <td>Day 90</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <p>Accounts are automatically deleted after the inactivity threshold. Associated personal data is removed
            from active systems. Backup data may be retained temporarily before permanent deletion. Certain data may
            be retained longer where required for legal obligations, security, dispute resolution, or operational backups.</p>

            <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul class="mb-3">
                <li>Access your data (in-app export available)</li>
                <li>Correct your data</li>
                <li>Delete your account</li>
                <li>Restrict or object to processing</li>
            </ul>
            <p>These controls are available within your account settings, or by contacting us via our privacy email.</p>

            <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Children's Data</h2>
            <p>The platform may be used by individuals under 18. Stricter retention rules apply (30-day inactivity limit)
            and automatic deletion is enforced for inactive accounts.</p>

            <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Data Sharing</h2>
            <ul class="mb-3">
                <li>No sale of personal data</li>
                <li>No sharing for advertising or tracking purposes</li>
                <li>Limited sharing with infrastructure providers only (hosting, delivery)</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Security</h2>
            <ul class="mb-3">
                <li>HTTPS encryption in transit</li>
                <li>Secure authentication mechanisms</li>
                <li>Access control and role-based permissions</li>
                <li>Industry-standard password hashing</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Compliance</h2>
            <p>This platform aligns with:</p>
            <ul class="mb-3">
                <li>GDPR (EU)</li>
                <li>Australian Privacy Principles (APP)</li>
                <li>CCPA/CPRA (where applicable — no sale or share model)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Key principles: data minimisation, storage limitation, transparency, user control, and security by design.</p>

            <div class="alert alert-primary rounded-4 mt-4 mb-0">
                <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-text me-2"></i>
                For the full Privacy Policy, visit
                <a href="https://repasscloud.com/legal/privacy-policy/aethonsoftware"
                   target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="alert-link">
                    repasscloud.com/legal/privacy-policy/aethonsoftware
                </a>.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
        <button onclick="history.back()" class="btn btn-outline-dark rounded-4 px-4">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-2"></i>Go back
        </button>
    </div>
</div>
